{"type": "article", "id": 6263, "title": "行尸走肉 The Walking Dead", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 3603, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;\">《行尸走肉》毫无疑问是这几年最火爆的美剧，瑞克团队的聚散离合让人揪心不已，而这部同名游戏就是其衍生作品。不过，虽然和瑞克团队处在同一个世界中，这个游戏却讲述了另一群人的故事。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604214007QujIHvcRpAgJ9O8f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t游戏主要通过选择不同的对话来推进<span style=\"color:#000000;\">剧情，你的每一个选择都会将故事引向不同的结局。游戏带入感很强，它将人性放置在冷冰冰的砧板上，而你就是屠夫。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0px;color:#737373;font-family:'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13px;white-space:normal;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#000000;\">游戏现在出到第二季，感兴趣的同学可以在 </span><a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/search/?snr=1_5_9__12&amp;term=the+walking+dead\" style=\"-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;color:#0069D6;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\">Steam</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000;\"> 上购买。</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}